    "improvements_made": "Added missing entities (ROLE, CONTENT_VERSION, STATE_HISTORY) and enriched attributes for auditability (updated_at, updated_by, change_summary, is_active flags, content_type, etc.). Introduced many‑to‑many relationships for role‑permission and user‑role management, and for workflow‑state definitions. Added STATE_HISTORY to capture state transitions with timestamps and comments. Expanded LOG to store operation details. Included COMMENT threading support. Strengthened referential integrity by explicitly linking current_state_id and workflow_id in CONTENT. Overall model now fully supports versioning, detailed audit trails, permission hierarchies, and workflow state management."
